
=== Welcome ===================================================================

  ** app. location **
    /opt/app --> main app.

  In order to update this app. from inside the container
    - supervisorctl stop all
    - git clone <url.git> <some_dir>
    - rsync -av <some_dir>/app /opt/
    - supervisorctl start all

  Logs
    - tailf /var/log/supervisor/dashboard.log
    - tailf /var/log/supervisor/backend.log
    - tailf /var/log/supervisor/dashboard_setup.log
    - tailf /var/log/supervisor/backend_setup.log

===============================================================================

